Why are you getting so close?

00:05:17.200 --> 00:05:18.640
I can’t see it.

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:22.200
Why didn’t you find a better place, somewhere with more space?

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:25.800
Shh! Do you want Captain to find out and sack us out of the camp?

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:34.040
The cause of death is drowning because there were trace of water found in the lungs.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:39.720
He probably died from suffocation because of the water in his lungs.

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:46.480
High possibility of suicide.

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:50.760
But Captain Akk thought he was silenced.

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:57.680
So, Captain Akk definitely knows what operation Lieut Tam was doing.

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:02.360
But in this case file, it says that…

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:08.720
there are bruises around his body, arms, and legs. There’s a mark that looks like he was hit by a solid object too.

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:12.400
But it doesn’t say what the actual cause is.

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:18.400
If Lieut Tam was killed…

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:24.600
why did the culprit dump his body around our camp?

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:27.880
Wasn’t that too risky?

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:34.720
It might be a warning…

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:41.520
to let us know that they knew about Lieut Tam’s real identity, that he disguised himself as a drug dealer.

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:47.159
Yeah.

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:57.760
What did you find?

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:06.720
I think this knot on his ankles…

00:07:07.960 --> 00:07:09.960
Lieut Tam didn’t tie it by himself.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.280
How do you know?

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.040
I just know.

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:20.280
Tell me.

00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:22.280
[Sound of door opening]

00:07:24.640 --> 00:07:26.360
Where are you going? Come back here.

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:06.640
I’m sleepy. Go back to your bed.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.400
No, I’m not leaving…

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:20.080
until you’d tell me.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:31.640
Then sleep here tonight.

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:33.960
I happen to be in need of a bolster.

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:36.760
Let me go.

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:38.679
Let me go.

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:40.760
Let me go.

00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:42.559
Sleep here.

