The instructor is coming!

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:08.560
Are you going to be my bolster?

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:12.960
Just get your sleep.

00:09:15.400 --> 00:09:16.560
Where are you going, bolster?

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:17.760
Sleep!

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:32.560
(Whistle sound)

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:34.280
Hooya!

00:09:52.520 --> 00:09:53.640
Go!

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.400
Tharn.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:28.320
I dreamt that you and Phaya were cuddling on his bed.

00:10:28.760 --> 00:10:31.920
As if you guys were doing something intimacy.

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:36.120
It was just a dream.

00:10:38.520 --> 00:10:40.080
Cut it out and get ready for the class.

00:10:40.880 --> 00:10:41.800
Fine, fine.

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:26.600
Sit down.

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:39.600
Open your book and turn to page 24.

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:43.360
Section 4: Criminal Liability.

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:47.120
Let’s see the definition of deliberated or intentional act or behaviour.

00:11:58.960 --> 00:12:04.160
It’s the act or behaviour committed intentionally while being well aware of such act or behaviour.

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:08.800
If such act or behaviour is committed by negligence, it is not considered as deliberated act or behaviour.

00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:16.360
Left, left, left, left…

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:42.720
- 8, 9, 10.
- Together.

00:13:04.920 --> 00:13:06.680
That kick was really awesome.

00:13:06.800 --> 00:13:07.880
I almost couldn’t get back up.

00:13:07.880 --> 00:13:08.760
Tharn.

00:13:09.240 --> 00:13:10.120
Water.

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:13.160
Thanks.

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.000
No problem.

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:20.080
Hey.

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:23.360
You guys are getting better.

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:24.800
Let’s hear it for yourself.

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:27.040
- Thank you, sir. / - Thank you.

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:28.160
Keep trying

00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:29.040
I’m sorry about earlier, sir.

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:29.880
It’s all right. You did good.

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:35.880
Geez, I thought we’d be able to relax a bit after that hellish week of training.

00:13:36.640 --> 00:13:39.240
Nothing has come into my head since the morning class.

00:13:39.600 --> 00:13:41.680
Holding a gun and hunting down criminals is enough for a police officer.

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:44.080
Can we talk?

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:00.640
What do you want?

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:03.440
Don’t you want to find out more about Lieut Tam case? About that knot?

00:14:03.640 --> 00:14:04.520
Sit down.

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:05.320
Sit.

00:14:05.320 --> 00:14:07.240
- I’m leaving.
- Sit down, Tharn.

00:14:07.520 --> 00:14:08.360
Sit.

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:11.640
Sit still.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:14.720
Put your legs together.

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:19.880
What are you doing?

00:14:20.640 --> 00:14:23.280
Just stay still and watch. Don’t you want to know the truth?

00:14:25.840 --> 00:14:31.480
If Lieut Tam really wanted to kill himself, he’d have tied a knot like this.

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:34.160
But look.

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:39.080
This is the photo I took from the case file.

00:14:41.560 --> 00:14:45.840
The knot tied by yourself and by the other will look completely different.

00:14:46.600 --> 00:14:52.640
If Lieut Tam committed suicide, the knot must be at the front.

00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:55.560
But in this photo, the knot is at the back.

00:14:56.280 --> 00:14:57.960
This means someone else must tie it for him.

00:14:58.400 --> 00:14:59.160
Exactly.

00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:03.880
Let’s tell Captain Akk about this.

00:15:05.880 --> 00:15:07.360
We still don’t have enough evidence.

00:15:07.880 --> 00:15:10.880
Didn’t you hear what Captain said? The authority ordered him to have this case closed.

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:16.720
This means the one behind Lieut Tam’s death must be very powerful.

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:19.560
We must gather more evidence.

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:25.520
But if we need more evidence, will just the two of us capable enough?

00:15:27.720 --> 00:15:29.360
It’s five of us.

00:15:33.880 --> 00:15:36.040
Spill everything out right now.

00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:58.840
Did you know Lieut Tam before coming to this camp?

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:01.960
He was my senior at the university.

00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:06.800
When I heard that he killed himself because of the gambling debt, I didn’t believe a single word of it.

00:16:07.200 --> 00:16:09.600
Before Lieut Tam joined the special investigation team,

00:16:09.720 --> 00:16:13.680
he was one of the best in arresting the criminal gangs for operating online gambling and drug trafficking.

00:16:14.200 --> 00:16:16.240
And from what I heard from other instructors,

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:21.800
on the night before his death, he was seen around his lodging.

00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:23.880
But he didn’t report himself at the camp.

00:16:26.880 --> 00:16:30.720
Khem, are you investigating about this case too?

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:34.720
Thongthai and I sneaked out to

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:39.240
The door was locked. There was lots of dust on the lock too.

00:16:40.640 --> 00:16:44.920
If Lieut Tam was really seen around there that night, he should be back in his lodging, shouldn’t he?

00:16:47.760 --> 00:16:50.160
What if it wasn’t Lieut Tam who was at the lodging?

00:16:50.560 --> 00:16:53.600
It was probably someone who tried to fabricate the false evidence.

00:16:57.960 --> 00:17:01.240
Then we have to start from finding out who that person is.

00:17:04.040 --> 00:17:07.400
But it’s not easy at all.

00:17:09.240 --> 00:17:11.079
How are we going to find some time to investigate on this?

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:15.119
We barely have enough time to rest with all those trainings and classes.

00:17:15.800 --> 00:17:16.960
Also,

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:22.560
If Captain Akk finds out, we’d probably get sacked.

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:35.320
I’m not forcing anyone to do it.

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:39.560
But I’m going to do it.

00:17:40.800 --> 00:17:42.800
I’ve decided to become a cop.

00:17:43.600 --> 00:17:45.360
If I ignore this,

00:17:46.280 --> 00:17:48.080
I won’t deserve to be called a police officer.

00:17:54.480 --> 00:17:55.640
Then I’ll do it too.

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:01.400
If he’s in then I’m also in.

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:04.120
Me too.

00:18:20.560 --> 00:18:24.000
Tharn, are you sure?

00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:26.840
Just one false move,

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:32.080
your dream for joining the special investigation force in order to investigate about your dad’s death would all be shattered.

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:37.560
If you do something good, some good things will surely happen to you.

00:18:38.440 --> 00:18:40.720
Think of it as a test before we’d officially become a cop.

00:19:39.760 --> 00:19:41.480
What are they doing here?

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:44.840
They said they lost something at the beach.

00:19:45.280 --> 00:19:48.000
So, they asked if they could check the CCTV camera dated 2 days back.

00:19:49.240 --> 00:19:50.920
2 nights ago?

00:20:18.520 --> 00:20:20.880
I’ve checked the CCTV camera.

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:22.920
I couldn’t see Lieut Tam anywhere.

00:20:33.080 --> 00:20:36.600
What did you say? Thongthai and Kem wanted to see the island map?

00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:38.160
Yes, sir.

00:21:12.600 --> 00:21:20.240
Baby
Baby and I got new information.
Baby, tell them what we’ve got.

00:21:22.920 --> 00:21:23.960
Don't you see it?

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:41.880
I did some research on the tidal pattern of the sea level.

00:21:42.400 --> 00:21:48.800
There are 2 tidal patterns in the Gulf of Thailand
Diurnal tides and Mixed tides.

00:21:49.200 --> 00:21:53.680
In the Andaman, it’s only Semidiurnal tides.

00:21:55.400 --> 00:22:00.440
Wow, you’re so good at this, Baby. How come I never knew it before.

00:22:00.600 --> 00:22:03.320
Because you were always falling asleep in class.

00:22:04.320 --> 00:22:08.160
Absolutely right.
Geez.

00:22:10.240 --> 00:22:14.480
I checked the CCTV on the day
that Lieut Tam was said to be seen near his lodging.

00:22:15.360 --> 00:22:16.960
I couldn’t see him anywhere.

00:22:19.440 --> 00:22:24.160
Let’s compare the info you’ve got with the night
that Lieut Tam was said to commit suicide.

00:22:25.320 --> 00:22:26.920
There was a depression that night.

00:22:28.360 --> 00:22:34.080
Suppose Lieut Tam did commit suicide on the beach,
it was impossible to find his body on the shore.

00:22:35.800 --> 00:22:37.000
Unless…

00:22:38.160 --> 00:22:42.920
he killed himself at the other side of this island.
The tide would then carry his body back to shore.

00:22:44.960 --> 00:22:50.920
Then we need to find more evidence there.

00:22:51.680 --> 00:22:57.840
Do you really think there’d be anything left for you to find out there?
Well, in case the evidence lies under the sea.

00:22:58.280 --> 00:23:01.720
The body was carried by the tides, wasn’t it?
It didn’t fall down from the sky.

00:23:03.320 --> 00:23:06.720
Why are you surprised?

00:23:07.360 --> 00:23:11.040
I did learn about it, you know.
Shut up, Khem.

00:23:11.400 --> 00:23:13.080
I need to think.

00:24:44.160 --> 00:24:46.200
Master Phaya.

00:24:53.200 --> 00:24:55.120
Master Phaya.

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:15.720
Master Sakunanopparuj, this way please.

00:26:41.800 --> 00:26:42.880
Phaya!

00:26:43.360 --> 00:26:44.280
Phaya!

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:46.320
What the hell are you doing, Phaya?

00:26:48.760 --> 00:26:49.720
Phaya.

00:26:52.520 --> 00:26:53.280
Phaya.

00:26:59.200 --> 00:27:00.200
Th…Tharn.

00:27:06.000 --> 00:27:07.080
That voice…

00:27:08.640 --> 00:27:09.840
Was it you?

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:11.640
What are you talking about?

00:27:11.760 --> 00:27:13.000
Get yourself together.

00:27:24.840 --> 00:27:25.800
Tharn.

00:27:31.320 --> 00:27:35.280
Why do you look like that person in my dream?

00:27:42.880 --> 00:27:44.480
What are you trying to do?

00:27:47.560 --> 00:27:50.080
Do you think you’re a real officer now?

00:27:50.800 --> 00:27:51.560
No, sir.

00:27:52.000 --> 00:27:55.920
But isn’t it our job as a police officer to find out the truth?

00:27:56.040 --> 00:27:56.720
Is it?

00:27:57.040 --> 00:27:58.960
But I don’t see any police officer here.

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:03.040
Being a cop isn’t just about showing off or being mister smarty pants.

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:09.840
Do you really understand the meaning of ‘duty’?!
Or ‘rules and regulations?! Or even ‘discipline’?!

00:28:12.200 --> 00:28:15.240
Just do your job and mind your own business!

00:28:17.200 --> 00:28:23.280
But we did all that
because we wanted to proof Lieut Tam didn’t kill himself.

00:28:24.080 --> 00:28:25.840
You also think the same too, don’t you.

00:28:29.520 --> 00:28:32.040
What I think about this case is none of your business.

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:38.160
If you want to become a real cop,
you must learn to be responsible for your job.
Know your job and do your best with it.

00:28:42.640 --> 00:28:46.240
What you did tonight is a serious breach of discipline.

00:28:47.080 --> 00:28:49.680
If I find you doing anything like this again,

00:28:51.920 --> 00:28:53.440
you will not get another second chance.

00:28:56.080 --> 00:28:58.000
you will be expelled immediately!

00:28:58.440 --> 00:28:59.200
Got it?

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:01.200
Hooya!

00:29:01.880 --> 00:29:02.680
Do you get it?!

00:29:02.720 --> 00:29:03.800
Hooya!

00:29:09.320 --> 00:29:10.800
And not just the two of them.

00:29:11.640 --> 00:29:15.840
But including everyone who takes part in this silly game too.

00:29:23.120 --> 00:29:25.400
If you know that your name is in here,

00:29:25.920 --> 00:29:27.440
come to the front.

00:29:29.280 --> 00:29:30.120
NOW!

00:29:51.800 --> 00:29:54.680
You all have committed a shameful act
by violating the camp regulations…

00:29:57.080 --> 00:29:59.480
and disobeyed your superior’s orders.

00:30:02.440 --> 00:30:05.200
It is considered a serious breach of discipline.

00:30:06.520 --> 00:30:09.360
You have no rights to stick your nose
into the official authority’s business.

00:30:14.720 --> 00:30:16.600
If you really think you are good enough…

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:22.080
and want to bring justice to Lieut Tam,

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:25.320
just do your best in what you’re assigned to do.

00:30:26.320 --> 00:30:27.640
Pass the exam and become a real cop.

00:30:32.880 --> 00:30:34.080
I’ll keep watching to see…

00:30:36.360 --> 00:30:40.800
if a smartass who is crying for justice like you…

00:30:42.560 --> 00:30:44.280
Would only bark but not bite.

00:30:48.600 --> 00:30:51.080
And since you’ve done something wrong tonight,

00:30:51.840 --> 00:30:56.200
you will be punished so that the others will not follow suit.

00:30:58.600 --> 00:31:00.480
Prepare for stress position!

00:31:00.600 --> 00:31:01.680
Hooya!

00:31:11.640 --> 00:31:16.960
Captain, I’ve looked at the evidence that
those kids could find. They were quite good.

00:31:18.800 --> 00:31:23.480
It’d be great if they can join the special investigation team.

00:31:27.080 --> 00:31:31.280
It doesn’t matter how talented they are,
if they can’t follow the rules and be disciplined…

00:31:33.040 --> 00:31:34.440
those talents are just a waste.

00:31:56.520 --> 00:31:57.320
Guys,

00:32:07.120 --> 00:32:08.000
I’m…

00:32:11.560 --> 00:32:12.520
I’m really sorry.

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:16.720
for making us all in trouble.

00:32:22.480 --> 00:32:23.480
It’s all right.

00:32:25.520 --> 00:32:27.120
Just forget it.

00:32:27.920 --> 00:32:29.000
What’s done is done.

00:32:29.400 --> 00:32:30.160
Yeah.

00:32:30.840 --> 00:32:35.360
We were acting like a smartass just like what Captain said.

00:32:39.840 --> 00:32:42.040
I think what he said was actually right.

00:32:43.360 --> 00:32:48.360
For us to become a good cop, we stick to the rules

00:32:50.160 --> 00:32:52.560
Starting from passing the exam first.

