Shit, whose car is it?

01:03:12.640 --> 01:03:15.080
- Dr. Chalothorn.
- Tharn.

01:03:16.680 --> 01:03:17.560
Excuse me?

01:03:39.320 --> 01:03:43.240
Tharn and I have known Dr. Chalothorn since we were young.

01:03:43.520 --> 01:03:47.280
Good for him. Now, he’d someone to take care of him when he’s drunk.

01:03:49.560 --> 01:03:55.640
Grandma, maybe it’s time for me to find out…

01:03:55.680 --> 01:03:58.240
what those dreams actually mean.

01:03:58.560 --> 01:04:02.720
I’m going to start from where it begins – where all those dreams started.

01:04:02.720 --> 01:04:04.080
Phaya.

01:04:05.360 --> 01:04:08.520
Tharn. Why are you here?

01:04:23.800 --> 01:04:31.400
🎵I will always cherish this love in my heart.🎵

01:04:31.400 --> 01:04:47.360
🎵No matter for how long, I’ll always want to see you.🎵
🎵I want you to know that you are the one that I want.🎵

01:04:47.360 --> 01:04:57.320
🎵I’m going to love you and only you.🎵

01:04:57.720 --> 01:05:12.720
🎵No matter for how lond, it will never change.🎵
🎵Whether in my sleep or while I’m awake.🎵
🎵I’ll never forget you.🎵

01:05:12.720 --> 01:05:20.000
🎵No matter for how long, I’ll always love you.🎵

01:05:20.200 --> 01:05:24.200
🎵Love you with all my heart.🎵

01:05:24.400 --> 01:05:32.120
🎵No one can take your place because my heart belongs to you.🎵